      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented justification for continuum FEA representation of screw-rod construct; constitutive model selection supported by material characterization data.",
      "rationale": "Continuum FEA with bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity for titanium alloy components is well-established for pedicle screw constructs. Material constants derived from Ti-6Al-4V tensile coupon data consistent with ASTM F136. Model form uncertainty quantified as part of validation comparison."
